snippet.title: Seaside Cafe Story (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Cook good food, build a nice cafe, and serve happy customers. Do you have what it takes to build a comfy culinary paradise on a tropical island? Test your skills as a chef and cafe owner in this refreshing lite management game!

Demo available on:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1398080/Seaside_Cafe_Story/
itch: https://studio-namaapa.itch.io/seaside-cafe
Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/seasidecafe/543015
